Compile the program with the 'make' or 'gmake' (on BSD) command and copy the
agim binary to any location in your $PATH. There is currently no support for
automatic installation.


Dependencies:

wireless-tools (http://www.hpl.hp.com/personal/Jean_Tourrilhes/Linux/Tools.html)
	(Only on Linux)


Compile-time dependencies:

GNU make
GCC
